<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Nkosis sikelel 'l Afrika
 We ask your peace O God for Africa
 I see the millions standing by my side
 Sotho Zulu Xhosa and Shangaan
 Give us your blessing
 God let us be one
 Marching hand in hand across our land
 Through fields of agony, prosperity
 Reaching out for all to see
 That God restores the broken Fatherland
 Nkosi sikelel 'l Afrika
 We ask your peace of God for Africa
 Sotho Zulu Xhosa and Shangaan
 Nkosi, Nkosi, Nkosi sikelel 'l Afrika</lyrics>
<title>Nkosi</title>
<author>Evan Schoombie</author>
<hymn_number>304</hymn_number>
</song>